  <body>

  <p>This is a meta model class.</p>
  <p>
Someone or something that can act purposefully. It may be a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_meta_organisation">META ORGANISATION</xref>
, a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_meta_person">META PERSON</xref>
 or person playing a role. - The 'someone' may be a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_meta_care_professional">META CARE PROFESSIONAL</xref>
 such as a specific GP, or a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_meta_person">META PERSON</xref>
/
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_meta_care_professional">META CARE PROFESSIONAL</xref>
 playing a 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_meta_person_role_in_organisation">META PERSON ROLE IN ORGANISATION</xref>
, for example Mr Smith, Consultant cardiologist, St Elsewheres Hospital Trust.  </p>
  <p>
Sub types of 
    <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_meta_agent">META AGENT</xref>
 include:  </p>
